WEBVTT

00:06:00.726 --> 00:06:04.393
ili kuwepo na uhaba huo wa ufanisi
katika nchi ya kiafrika,

00:06:04.417 --> 00:06:05.777
lazima kuwe na rushwa.

00:06:06.491 --> 00:06:09.967
Seli kuu husika lazima iwe inahusishwa na rushwa.

00:06:10.972 --> 00:06:12.504
Nilidhani hivyo, pia.

00:06:12.984 --> 00:06:14.137
Tulipoanza,

00:06:14.161 --> 00:06:17.649
Nilitarajia kukuta rushwa nyingi katika mfumo,

00:06:17.673 --> 00:06:21.169
Nilihisi ningekufa ama kuuawa katika mchakato.

00:06:21.193 --> 00:06:22.736
(Vicheko)

00:06:24.946 --> 00:06:26.901
Lakini tulipochunguza kiundani,

00:06:26.925 --> 00:06:29.560
hatukukuta rushwa katika maana ya kawaida: